The people have 4 different jobs:  chef, manager, nurse, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, disaster, thriller
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, writing, card-games, singing
There are 4 different favourite colors: black, mauve, aquamarine, ebony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, ice-hockey, skateboarding, swimming
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3
 2. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who likes mauve##2
 3. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is the colonial house##1
 5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 6. the person who likes mauve is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person watching disaster movies is on the left of the colonial house##1
 8. the teacher is the tower house##1
 9. the townhouse house is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's sport is skateboarding##2
10. the chef is on the left of the nurse##1
11. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who likes mauve##1
12. the person drinking lemonade is on the left or right of the person who likes black##3
13. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
14. the craftsman house is on the far right##1
15. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
16. the person watching thriller movies is the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
17. the person watching disaster movies is on the left or right of the chef##3

.:: Answer ::.
