 1. the owner of the cat is on the far left or far right##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in february is the bartender##1
 3. the person eating lemon is the person watching drama movies##1
 4. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person eating cranberry is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york##3
 6. the architect is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 7. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 8. the owner of the horse is on the left or right of the person traveling to hamburg##3
 9. the italian is on the left or right of the owner of the turtle##3
10. the person eating pumpkin is on the far right##1
11. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left of the person traveling to prague##1
12. the person who's birthday is in november is the person traveling to new-york##1
13. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person eating cranberry##1
14. the chinese is the owner of the horse##1
15. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the canadian##1
16. the person watching musical movies is the nurse##1
17. the person watching drama movies is the bartender##1
18. the canadian is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
